00:00:33.820 --> 00:00:35.780
=Lust and Lies=

00:00:42.840 --> 00:00:43.920
The Lion Seal is lost.

00:00:44.719 --> 00:00:45.640
Huo Xiu has run away.

00:00:48.840 --> 00:00:49.439
If so,

00:00:49.479 --> 00:00:51.920
I'll look into it on your behalf.

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:54.479
Yes, sir.

00:01:27.120 --> 00:01:29.799
This was found in the account
at Henglong Bank.

00:01:29.920 --> 00:01:31.000
Did you expect to see

00:01:31.120 --> 00:01:33.079
some immeasurable wealth
in this account as well?

00:01:39.159 --> 00:01:40.519
What's inside this briefcase

00:01:41.439 --> 00:01:44.280
is the most important wealth to us.

00:01:48.079 --> 00:01:48.680
My mother

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:50.840
never stopped trying
to clean my father's name

00:01:51.200 --> 00:01:52.560
and exposing Huo Beishan.

00:01:55.239 --> 00:01:56.280
She hid all evidence

00:01:57.040 --> 00:01:58.400
in this briefcase.

00:01:58.879 --> 00:01:59.879
That means

00:02:00.519 --> 00:02:03.400
the rumor about the Lion Seal is fake.

00:02:05.120 --> 00:02:05.879
Changqing.

00:02:06.159 --> 00:02:08.280
I've spread the word about the Lion Seal.

00:02:10.240 --> 00:02:12.280
The human heart is greedy.

00:02:13.159 --> 00:02:16.879
Everyone will be greedy enough
to fight over the Lion Seal.

00:02:19.120 --> 00:02:21.680
When the fortune is found,

00:02:22.560 --> 00:02:23.800
that will be the day

00:02:24.599 --> 00:02:27.240
the Huo family meets their demise.

00:02:34.360 --> 00:02:35.160
Mother.

00:02:35.759 --> 00:02:36.560
Mother.

00:02:36.719 --> 00:02:37.639
Are you alright?

00:02:39.159 --> 00:02:39.840
Xiu.

00:02:40.360 --> 00:02:41.000
Listen up.

00:02:41.319 --> 00:02:42.520
If I die,

00:02:43.759 --> 00:02:45.400
you must keep searching for evidence.

00:02:46.479 --> 00:02:48.719
You must watch the Huo family

00:02:50.479 --> 00:02:52.039
fall into disgrace.

00:02:55.290 --> 00:02:57.290
What a brilliant plot, you've managed
to keep your hands clean.

00:02:57.320 --> 00:02:59.000
You've actually been doing this
for so many years.

00:03:00.060 --> 00:03:01.790
You've put up with all
in the Huo Residence for so long

00:03:02.199 --> 00:03:03.479
to search for evidence?

00:03:07.599 --> 00:03:08.439
Boss Ruan

00:03:10.280 --> 00:03:11.680
never told you what happened back then?

00:03:12.240 --> 00:03:14.759
Father only said that Huo Beishan
wanted to silence witnesses,

00:03:15.240 --> 00:03:16.759
so he set our house on fire.

00:03:17.479 --> 00:03:18.439
As for the reason,

00:03:18.680 --> 00:03:19.879
he never once mentioned it.

00:03:26.360 --> 00:03:27.680
It's fortunate you're not Huo Qingwan.

00:03:34.439 --> 00:03:35.719
And luckily, you don't bear the Huo name.

00:04:14.060 --> 00:04:15.900
=Episode 20=

00:04:31.759 --> 00:04:32.399
Mr. Sheng.

00:04:33.279 --> 00:04:33.959
Mr. Sheng.

00:04:34.319 --> 00:04:35.680
You know you adore Miss Qingwan.

00:04:35.800 --> 00:04:37.000
Only you can save her now.

00:04:37.500 --> 00:04:38.079
Why did you say so?

00:04:38.260 --> 00:04:39.480
Governor has dispatched the hitmen.

00:04:39.680 --> 00:04:40.800
The Huo Army is also on its way there.

00:04:42.879 --> 00:04:43.959
You want me

00:04:44.319 --> 00:04:45.199
to save Huo Xiu together?

00:04:48.560 --> 00:04:49.000
Fine.

00:04:49.360 --> 00:04:50.000
I'll go save him.

00:04:51.639 --> 00:04:52.279
Thank you.

00:05:00.839 --> 00:05:02.600
You actually believed what I said.

00:05:05.560 --> 00:05:07.839
With idiots like you around him,

00:05:08.279 --> 00:05:09.439
no wonder Huo Xiu is all useless.

00:05:12.040 --> 00:05:13.079
Don't you know

00:05:13.199 --> 00:05:15.000
the one I hate most is Huo Xiu?

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:19.040
You heard it all on that day, no?

00:05:20.000 --> 00:05:21.759
The conversation
between me and Governor.

00:05:26.759 --> 00:05:28.079
You're going to silence me?

00:05:35.360 --> 00:05:38.560
Young Marshal,
you're truly a skilled shooter.

00:05:39.199 --> 00:05:40.680
Put the gun down slowly.

00:05:48.720 --> 00:05:49.720
Hurry up!

00:05:54.079 --> 00:05:54.800
That's it.

00:05:55.519 --> 00:05:56.600
Slowly.

00:05:57.240 --> 00:05:58.279
That's the way it is.

00:06:01.720 --> 00:06:02.600
Goodbye!

00:06:03.560 --> 00:06:04.079
Feifei!

00:06:22.020 --> 00:06:27.380
♪It's you in the blur
of light and shadow♪

00:06:28.700 --> 00:06:34.580
♪Our first encounter
left me in awe for a lifetime♪

00:06:35.780 --> 00:06:39.820
♪Feelings I can't shake off♪

00:06:39.820 --> 00:06:42.420
♪Quietly emerge♪

00:06:42.420 --> 00:06:48.300
♪It was just a single glance♪

00:06:49.100 --> 00:06:52.420
♪A moment apart feels like endless years♪

00:06:52.420 --> 00:06:56.380
♪Amidst the light and shadow♪

00:06:56.700 --> 00:06:59.500
♪Love and hate blur together♪

00:06:59.500 --> 00:07:02.460
♪Why let ourselves fall deeper
than we already are?♪

00:07:03.399 --> 00:07:04.319
You're finally awake.

00:07:07.600 --> 00:07:08.480
I thought

00:07:08.879 --> 00:07:10.360
- I'd lose you.
- I'd lose you.

00:07:10.360 --> 00:07:12.060
♪You remain the same♪

00:07:12.060 --> 00:07:17.340
♪A longing I can never get over,
like mist, like dreams♪

00:07:18.240 --> 00:07:19.319
I won't let you die on me.

00:07:21.319 --> 00:07:21.959
What's the matter?

00:07:25.120 --> 00:07:26.000
Cheng is missing.

00:07:34.759 --> 00:07:36.639
He's the only one
I can trust in the residence.

00:07:39.160 --> 00:07:40.360
He's my closest brother.

00:07:43.920 --> 00:07:44.680
I understand.

00:07:45.839 --> 00:07:47.040
Just like Zhao Xun.

00:07:48.480 --> 00:07:49.720
He was the kindest to me

00:07:49.879 --> 00:07:50.800
in the Huofeng Gang.

00:08:01.000 --> 00:08:01.879
Huo Beishan.

00:08:03.720 --> 00:08:05.120
He must pay for what he did to them.

00:08:30.399 --> 00:08:32.200
These are the arms you moved

00:08:32.960 --> 00:08:34.400
during the festival
to welcome the deity?

00:08:35.120 --> 00:08:35.559
Yes.

00:08:36.919 --> 00:08:38.240
Who would have thought

00:08:39.120 --> 00:08:40.200
they'd end up in your hands?

00:08:41.690 --> 00:08:42.679
Take your time to recuperate.

00:08:43.759 --> 00:08:46.799
I will avenge the Ruan family for you.

00:08:52.440 --> 00:08:53.519
Spare the First Madam.

00:08:59.919 --> 00:09:00.559
I think

00:09:01.200 --> 00:09:02.360
they've waited long

00:09:03.480 --> 00:09:04.600
for this day to come, no?

00:09:15.480 --> 00:09:17.159
The night is cold and damp.

