Relight the lantern.

00:09:36.440 --> 00:09:37.679
Newspaper for sale!

00:09:37.759 --> 00:09:39.159
Clearing the Gu family's name.

00:09:39.240 --> 00:09:40.720
The Huo family are in fact traitors.

00:09:40.799 --> 00:09:42.080
Newspaper for sale!

00:09:57.919 --> 00:09:58.320
Father.

00:10:00.720 --> 00:10:01.960
Sucheng has descended into chaos.

00:10:02.240 --> 00:10:03.159
We should leave together.

00:10:06.039 --> 00:10:07.320
Here comes the best opportunity,

00:10:07.960 --> 00:10:08.679
so I can't leave.

00:10:09.039 --> 00:10:10.200
If so, we'll put it in the papers soon

00:10:11.000 --> 00:10:12.490
and annul the engagement
with the Huo family.

00:10:12.879 --> 00:10:13.679
We shall sever our ties.

00:10:15.080 --> 00:10:15.360
No.

00:10:16.480 --> 00:10:17.120
Let's

00:10:17.600 --> 00:10:19.679
see how it goes and carry on
with the marriage alliance.

00:10:24.240 --> 00:10:25.840
That's a risky move.

00:10:27.440 --> 00:10:28.360
If we take a wrong step,

00:10:28.799 --> 00:10:29.960
we will lose everything.

00:10:34.039 --> 00:10:35.559
I intend to risk it all.

00:10:59.919 --> 00:11:00.440
Beishan.

00:11:02.879 --> 00:11:03.919
This time, is our family

00:11:04.720 --> 00:11:06.159
truly done for?

00:11:07.879 --> 00:11:08.480
It's done for?

00:11:17.799 --> 00:11:19.879
Despite all those rumors

00:11:20.000 --> 00:11:22.080
and them calling me a traitor,

00:11:23.000 --> 00:11:25.080
my family has numerous troops.

00:11:25.360 --> 00:11:26.720
Who dares oppose me?

00:11:30.200 --> 00:11:31.120
Guards,

00:11:31.360 --> 00:11:33.200
order all of the Huo Army

00:11:33.879 --> 00:11:35.279
to return to Sucheng!

